unities others may miss thats because we know success comes from encouraging our people to think differently our culture promotes innovation and entrepreneurial drive within a strong risk management framework our organisation macquarie is a diversified financial group providing clients with asset management and finance banking advisory and risk and capital solutions across debt equity and commodities the diversity of our operations combined with a strong capital position and robust risk management framework has contributed to our year record of unbroken profitability macquarie asset management corporate and asset finance group banking and financial services group commodities and global markets macquarie capital our organisation structure macquarie has a nonhierarchical organisational structure split into five operating groups the executive committee a central group comprising the managing director deputy managing director head of risk management global chief operation officer and heads of macquaries major operating groups manage the organisation as a whole individual businesses operate within macquaries operating groups these businesses work closely together specialising in defined product or market sectors and are committed to their clients relationship with the macquarie group within overall guidelines and a strong risk management framework the operating groups have substantial discretion in the way they manage their business activities great emphasis is placed on a clients relationship with macquarie as a whole four service groups provide the framework infrastructure and support that the operating groups require to manage their business these are the corporate operations financial management legal and governance and risk management groups   our support groups our businesses are supported by specialist global teams corporate operations group financial management group risk management group legal and governance leadership and corporate governance macquarie aims to 