xed income markets it typically invests in companies engaged in infrastructure activities or emerging market securities the firm employs a fundamental technical and charting analysis to make its investments it uses internal and external research to make its investments the firm was founded on january   and is based in the new york city macquarie capital investment management llc operates as a subsidiary of macquarie group limited detailed description  west th streetnew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  key executives for macquarie capital investment management llc mr jonathan aubrey fitch chief executive officer chief investment officer and portfolio manager age  ms meredith l meyer chief operating officer age  mr andrew maplebrown managing director portfolio manager and director mr bradford lee frishberg cfa head of global infrastructure securities team and portfolio manager age  mr jonathan hall compensation as of fiscal year  macquarie capital investment management llc key developments first trust advisors lp four corners capital management llc macquarie capital investment management llc  special call mar   first trust advisors lp four corners capital management llc macquarie capital investment management llc  special call four corners capital management llc macquariefirst trust global infrastructureutilities dividend  income fund macquarie capital investment management llc  special call aug   to provide an update on macquariefirst trust global infrastructureutilities dividend  income fund similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target private placement july   advanced microgrid solutions inc private placement december   laureate education inc request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp glo