etaining its intrinsic value with the two new coins – the holey dollar and the dump – worth  per cent more than the original according to macquarie group the ‘holey dollar’ was australia’s earliest example of ‘financial innovation’ and ‘embodies its pursuit of practical approaches with profitable outcomes’ criticismedit the companys high margins profits and the lucrative rewards for its executives and shareholders saw the australian media label the bank the millionaire factory due to their notably strong performances as of may   the groups chief executive nicholas moore became the nations highest paid ceo of a listed company as they announced a net profit after tax for the year at a billion macquarie group through its subsidiary macquarie equipment rentals has allegedly been perpetrating a telco finance scam macquarie equipment rentals has sued over  victims of the scam which involves bundling a finance equipment contract with a contract from a small telecommunications company often obscuring that the finance contract exists the scam involves the telecommunications company promising free equipment such as plasma tvs while offering a lower cost phone deal that offsets the cost of the equipment the victim is then tricked into signing two contracts with the true costs often hidden whilst being verbally promised that they will be free the telecommunications company is paid an upfront fee by the finance company and sometime later disappears the victim is then left with an inflated finance company lease that requires the victim to pay often tens of thousands of dollars for equipment that in reality costs a fraction of the price the companys high margins and profits and the rewards for its executives and shareholders saw the australian media label the bank the millionaire factory up until its share price fell almost  in early  see alsoedit companies portal australian real estate investment trust banking in australia better place list of banks list of banks in australia list of banks in oceania macquarie power  infrastructure income fund kemble water holdings limited macquarie airports southern cross media group referencesedit  thomsonreuterscom  developerthemonthlycomau  who’s afraid of macquarie bank the monthly retrieved    a b c developerthemonthlycomau  who’s afraid of macquarie bank the monthly retrieved    australia schemeaglstermsaglsagent corporatenamereserve bank of historical series breaks reserve bank of australia retrieved    partners message  australian  art gallery nsw wwwartgallerynswgovau retrieved    macquarie – how the mighty have changed  share trading  switzer wwwswitzercomau retrieved    newswires dow jones  macquarie bank to acquire unit of bankers trust australia wall street journal issn  retrieved    east  partners  macquarie snaps up ing’s asian equity business eastcomau retrieved    macquarie infrastructure company reports  results nysemic investorshareholdercom retrieved    muspratt by caroline lse rejects derisory macquarie bid telegraphcouk retrieved    macquarie wins as australia suffers from commodity rout bloombergcom  retrieved    the corona energy journey  corona energy corona energy retrieved    qantas takeover deal blocked  business  business  theagecomau wwwtheagecomau retrieved    macquarie bank limited receives final australian federal court approval for restructure of macquarie group pdf australian securities exchange    company profile  macquarie group   update macquarie tops  bln in commodities joining banks big league reuters  retrieved    macquarie to buy the boutique firm foxpitt kelton retrieved    mcfarland lyndal  macquarie to acquire delaware investments wall street journal issn  retrieved    macquarie groups delaware investments rebrands as macquarie investment management macquarie april   retrieved june     enbw sells offshore windpark stake to macquarie for  million euros reuters  january   macquarie to buy aircraft for  billion raise capital bloombergcom  retrieved    macquarieled 