llion inclusive of mcim’s affiliates globally is invested in both listed and private or direct infrastructure mandates as at june   fund highlights infrastructure a compelling longterm investment opportunity with attractive income and growth potential macquarie funds group world’s largest infrastructure asset manager with  billion of infrastructure under management quarterly distribution initially targeted at   pa outstanding track record strategy has consistently outperformed its benchmark exposure to a global portfolio of listed infrastructure securities effective august  aston hill capital markets will be the sole contact point for inquiries in relation to the macquarie global infrastructure income fund and the macquarie emerging markets infrastructure income fund collectively “the funds” please refer to httpastonhillcaclosedendfunds for further information on the funds important information security and privacy shareholder centre careers site map    macquarie global investments no entity within the macquarie group of companies is registered as a bank or an authorized foreign bank in canada under the bank act sc  c  and no entity within the macquarie group of companies is regulated in canada as a financial institution bank holding company or an insurance holding company macquarie bank limited abn     mbl is a company incorporated in australia and authorized under the banking act  australia to conduct banking business in australia mbl is not authorized to conduct business in canada no entity within the macquarie group of companies other than mbl is an authorized deposittaking institution for the purposes of the banking act  australia and their obligations do not represent deposits or other liabilities of mbl mbl does not guarantee or otherwise provide assurance in respect of the obligations of any other macquarie group company